body:
@freedomtan, @andrewharp , The prev model by following [this instructions](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/15633#issuecomment-377652630) can not work in [the latest TFLite Demo](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/examples/android), Whether it is quantified or float, because the tflite model in the latest TFLite demo requires 4 outputs , but prev model only have 2 outputs( concat, concat1).

Please help , Thanks!
